version_description: Im still here but the great Tom Waits. Some chords may be a little bit tricky. Enjoy.
There are no Chord versions of this song on Ultimate-Guitar, so I wrote one out, with some tablature at the start to help picking pattern.

This version includes the often overlooked diminished and augmented chords that complement the demented quality of the song (in addition to the awesome Tom vocals and detuned organ). Buy a round of beers before belting out this gem.
Neat formatting, alternating bass notes and chord legend included.
Complete intermediate version with split chords and suggestions for voicings / thoroughly ear-transcribed.
